RulesChat -> RulesChat : Build context:\n- MTG Comprehensive Rules\n- Relevant pattern knowledge\n- Active game state (if any)\n- Conversation history

RulesChat -> Patterns : Lookup matching patterns
Patterns -> DB : SELECT patterns\nWHERE keywords MATCH
DB --> Patterns : RelevantPattern[]
Patterns --> RulesChat : Pattern context

RulesChat -> RulesChat : Call AI with full context\nGenerate rules-accurate answer
RulesChat -> DB : INSERT question + answer
DB --> RulesChat : ok
RulesChat --> API : {answer, rules_refs[], confidence}
API --> Chat : Display answer with rule citations

opt Rate Answer
  User -> Chat : Rate answer quality
  Chat -> API : api.rateRulesAnswer(id, rating)
  API -> RulesChat : PUT /rules/qa-log-rate
  RulesChat -> DB : UPDATE rating
end

== Conversation History ==
User -> Chat : View past conversations
Chat -> API : api.getRulesConversations()
API -> Convos : GET /rules/conversations
Convos -> DB : SELECT conversations\nORDER BY updated_at DESC
DB --> Convos : Conversation[]
Convos --> API : conversation list
API --> Chat : Display conversation history

@enduml
